title: Irfan Shafi Khokhar wins PP-167
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz Irfan Shafi Khokhar has won the election from Punjab Assembly constituency PP-167 Lahore XXIII by securing 23,248 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Ammar Bashir who bagged 21,169 votes.
Votersâ€™ turn-out remained at 42.56 per cent.
